---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Trish Reske - Trish Reske's StoryLines Blog">
  <div id="content">
    <article class="post-card">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-serif text-[#600] mb-4">Trish Reske Bio</h1>

      <div class="overflow-hidden mb-4">
        <img src="/images/uploads/2009/02/Trish_Rome.jpg" alt="Trish Reske" class="float-right w-[200px] ml-4 mb-4 p-1 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200" />

        <div class="post-content">
          <p>
            My professional experience includes leading the creative efforts of three companies I have co-owned.
            I'm a seasoned copywriter/creative director, award-winning journalist, avid runner, and mom of four.
          </p>

          <p>
            Through my writing, I've explored topics ranging from parenting and running to business insights and travel.
            I believe in the power of storytelling to connect, inspire, and entertain.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-[#600] mt-6 mb-3">Education and Awards</h2>

          <p>
            Award-winning journalist published in numerous regional and national publications including
            <em>baystateparent magazine</em> and various community newspapers.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-[#600] mt-6 mb-3">Running</h2>

          <p>
            An avid marathoner, I've completed multiple Boston Marathons and have written extensively about
            the joy of running, training tips, and inspiring stories from the running community.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-[#600] mt-6 mb-3">Family</h2>

          <p>
            Mother of four wonderful children who have provided endless inspiration for my writing
            about parenting, family life, and the adventures of raising kids.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
